the San Francisco Giants at 5:05 p.m. PDT. 
By Brian Dohn. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBN-DODGERNOTES (San Francisco) _ Notebook from the Dodgers-Giants
game. 
By Brian Dohn. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBA-ANGELS-ATHLETICS (Anaheim, Calif.) _ The Anaheim Angels face
the Oakland A's at 5:05 p.m. PDT. 
By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBA-ANGELNOTES (Anaheim, Calif.) _ Notebook from the Angels-A's
game. 
By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
RAC-GOLDCUP (Inglewood, Calif.) _ Coverage of the Hollywood Gold
Cup. 
By Kevin Modesti. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
RAC-GOLDSIDE (Inglewood, Calif.) _ Sidebar from the Hollywood Gold
Cup. 
By Kevin Modesti. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
RUN-TRACK (Eugene, Ore.) _ U.S. Track and Field Championships,
focusing on Los Angeles-area athletes. 
By Kirby Lee. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
GEN-OFFBEAT (Los Angeles) _ Offbeat look at the week's sports
news. 
By Tom Hoffarth. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
GEN-CYBER (Los Angeles) _ Sports news from the internet. 
By Tom Hoffarth. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
GEN-TV (Los Angeles) _ A look at this week's TV highlights. 
By Tom Hoffarth. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
GEN-GLANCE (Los Angeles) _ A look at Los Angeles-area sports
history. 
By Tom Hoffarth. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 

