   Mission West Properties Inc., Cupertino, Calif., 6.75 million
shares. A.G. Edwards &AMP; Sons.
</P>
<P>
   Musicmaker.com, Reston, Va., an initial public offering of 8.4
million shares. Ferris Baker Watts Inc.
</P>
<P>
   National Medical Health Card Sys. Inc., Port Washington, N.Y.,
an initial public offering of 2.5 million shares. Ryan, Beck &AMP; Co.
</P>
