<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-27 21:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1281 &Cx1f; ttf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GRAPHICS-FILES-NYT &LR;      06-27 0151
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GRAPHICS-FILES-NYT </SLUG>
  
